Preheat #oven to 350 (325 if using a nonstick #baking sheet{}). Lightly grease sheet.

Place @Reese's Pieces Cookie Dough{1%unit} 2 inches apart on prepared sheet.

Bake until edges are set, ~{14-18%minutes}. (If baking from frozen dough, add 3 minutes to the bake time)

Cool cookies for ~{3%minutes} on sheet, then carefully transfer to a #plate. Serve.

> Pillsbury™ Mini REESE'S PIECES Cookie Dough: 12 Cookies

> No good meal is complete without a dessert! In this case, a batch of freshly baked, crispy-on-the-outside and gooey-on-the-inside cookies studded with Mini REESE'S PIECES. The best part, though? No mixing, no slicing, no mess—all you have to do is break, bake, and dig in.

> REESE'S PIECES trademark and trade dress and the REESE'S Orange Color are used under license.

> Nutrient values are representative of a 1 cookie serving. There are 12 servings per container.